		 Posted on   February 9, 2012  by  Ray Magnetic storage using lasers alone 	 
		 Lasers by dmuth (cc) (from Flickr) Read an article today on AAAS Science Now online magazine (See  Hot Idea for a Faster Hard Drive ) on using lasers alone to toggle magnetic moments in specially designed ferro-magnetic materials. 
